.\" -*-nroff-*-
.TH TASKMGR 1 "September 2014" "taskmgr 0.2" "taskmgr manual"
.SH NAME
taskmgr \- a lightweight GTK+ task manager.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B taskmgr
.SH DESCRIPTION
TaskMgr - lightweight and desktop-independent task manager derived from
xfce4-taskmanager with all dependencies on xfce removed, new features,
and some improvement of the user interface.
.SH OPTIONS
No options are supported by this program.
.SH AUTHOR
TaskMgr is derived from Xfce4 Task Manager.
Original authors of XFce4 Task Manager:
Johannes Zellner <webmaster@nebulon.de>,
